@adaptivetraining Seminar Weekend incoming! En route to Boston to educate, coach, and guide a new group of potential Adaptive and Inclusive Trainers. No question these are my favorite weekends!

Largely, they serve as a reminder for how lucky I am to have had so many incredible people in my corner, helping me discover all avenues of my potential. Being able to give back and share the same experiences to those around me is my “why”. I’m pretty darn okay with that.

#adaptive #coach #fitness #health #educate

